statements: SELECT * FROM property_market_data WHERE region = 'California'
SELECT region, sector, property_type FROM property_market_data WHERE demand > 100 AND supply < 50
SELECT average_price, region FROM property_market_data WHERE property_type = 'House' ORDER BY average_price DESC
SELECT * FROM property_market_data WHERE region = 'New York' AND sector = 'Commercial'
SELECT COUNT(*) as count FROM property_market_data
SELECT * FROM property_market_data WHERE region = 'New York' AND sector = 'Commercial';
SELECT region, sector, property_type, average_price FROM property_market_data WHERE demand > 100 AND supply < 50 ORDER BY region ASC, sector DESC;
SELECT region, sector, property_type, demand, supply FROM property_market_data WHERE average_price > 500000 ORDER BY demand DESC, average_price ASC;
SELECT sector, SUM(demand) AS total_demand, SUM(supply) AS total_supply FROM property_market_data GROUP BY sector HAVING total_demand > 500 AND total_supply < 300;
SELECT AVG(average_price) AS average_price, MAX(demand) AS max_demand, MIN(supply) AS min_supply FROM property_market_data WHERE region IN ('Paris', 'London', 'Berlin');
SELECT * FROM property_demand WHERE demand_level > 3
SELECT region_id, property_type FROM property_demand WHERE region_id = 2
SELECT property_type, demand_level FROM property_demand ORDER BY demand_level DESC
SELECT * FROM property_supply WHERE region_id = 5 AND supply_level < 10
SELECT region_id, property_type, supply_level FROM property_supply ORDER BY region_id
SELECT region_id, property_type, demand_level FROM property_demand WHERE region_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM property_demand WHERE property_type = 'house' ORDER BY demand_level DESC;
SELECT region_id, SUM(demand_level) AS total_demand FROM property_demand GROUP BY region_id;
SELECT region_id, property_type, supply_level FROM property_supply WHERE supply_level > 100 ORDER BY region_id ASC;
SELECT property_type, AVG(supply_level) AS avg_supply_level FROM property_supply GROUP BY property_type HAVING AVG(supply_level) > 50;
SELECT * FROM Region;
SELECT region_name, region_population FROM Region WHERE region_id = 1;
SELECT * FROM Property WHERE property_type = 'Residential';
SELECT property_id, property_type, property_area FROM Property ORDER BY property_area DESC;
SELECT market_data_id, property_id, forecast, date_recorded FROM MarketData WHERE demand_index > 50 AND supply_index < 30;
SELECT * FROM Region ORDER BY region_name DESC;
SELECT property_id, property_type, property_area FROM Property WHERE property_type = 'Residential';
SELECT region_name, region_population FROM Region WHERE region_population > 100000 ORDER BY region_population DESC;
SELECT market_data_id, demand_index, supply_index, forecast, date_recorded FROM MarketData WHERE date_recorded >= '2022-01-01' AND date_recorded <= '2022-12-31';
SELECT r.region_name, p.property_type, md.demand_index FROM Region r JOIN Property p ON r.region_id = p.region_id JOIN MarketData md ON p.property_id = md.property_id ORDER BY md.demand_index DESC;
SELECT * FROM property_demand;
SELECT region, demand_level FROM property_demand WHERE region='North';
SELECT property_id, region, supply_level FROM property_supply ORDER BY supply_level DESC;
SELECT region, year, demand_index, supply_index FROM market_fluctuations WHERE year > 2020;
SELECT * FROM investment_opportunities WHERE potential_roi > 0.05;
SELECT * FROM property_demand;
SELECT region, demand_level FROM property_demand WHERE demand_level > 5 ORDER BY region ASC;
SELECT property_id, region, supply_level FROM property_supply WHERE region = 'New York' ORDER BY supply_level DESC;
SELECT region, year, demand_index, supply_index FROM market_fluctuations WHERE year = 2021 AND demand_index > 50;
SELECT * FROM investment_opportunities WHERE region LIKE 'Cali%' ORDER BY potential_roi DESC;
SELECT * FROM Regions;
SELECT region_id, region_name FROM Regions ORDER BY region_name DESC;
SELECT property_name, property_size FROM Properties WHERE property_size > 100;
SELECT property_id, property_type, COUNT(*) AS demand_count FROM Demand GROUP BY property_id, property_type;
SELECT supply_date, supply_level FROM Supply WHERE supply_date BETWEEN '2022-01-01' AND '2022-03-31';
SELECT region_name, average_property_price FROM Regions;
SELECT * FROM Properties WHERE property_size > 100;

SELECT region_name, property_name, demand_level, demand_date FROM Regions r INNER JOIN Properties p ON r.region_id = p.region_id INNER JOIN Demand d ON p.property_id = d.property_id WHERE r.region_name = 'East';
SELECT p.property_name, i.investment_amount, i.investment_date FROM Properties p INNER JOIN Investments i ON p.property_id = i.property_id WHERE i.investment_amount > 50000;
SELECT DISTINCT r.region_name, p.property_type FROM Regions r INNER JOIN Properties p ON r.region_id = p.region_id WHERE p.property_type = 'Apartment';
